{"tid":570570,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企無啦啦多左個工人 係咪要養多個？","createTime":"2018-02-23T18:43:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-24T04:21:17.000Z","uid":97017,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9bbcfa1a34f3bce064cfc90ccd5aafbbe20c925c","tid":570570,"uid":97017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T18:43:02.000Z","msg":"話說我本身係識得照顧自己 <br />\n但係我媽又驚我無野食所以就請工人<br />\n但係請工人好那貴 一個月四千幾<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">包食包住</span><br />\n買乜都唔係用佢嘅錢 就連入八達通都係用我吖媽d錢！<br />\n佢每日整早餐 等我媽番工 佢就開始挽手機之後訓教仲要鎖門 當左間房係佢咁<br />\n新年仲跟住我媽去豆利是賭錢 每個月咁搵埋搵埋佢發達啦咁<br />\n有咩辦法送走佢吖Diu!<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9326208c6bdea447bd55f4e91370702a11068a4","tid":570570,"uid":151774,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T18:44:55.000Z","msg":"挽你老母對波 <br />\n幾千蚊跌都跌左啦<br />\n利申 屋企有兩個賓妹"},{"pid":"59b3590d03747e976824cf7ba679a6551ba6c373","tid":570570,"uid":167465,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T18:48:32.000Z","msg":"叫你媽俾4000你 你照顧埋你媽咪<br />\n咁佢就信你嫁喇 <br />\n仲要請走個工人tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2537ec78bb454757c2ede7952136d6d3e6fffe9","tid":570570,"uid":97017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59b3590d03747e976824cf7ba679a6551ba6c373","tid":570570,"uid":167465,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T18:48:32.000Z","msg":"叫你媽俾4000你 你照顧埋你媽咪<br />\n咁佢就信你嫁喇 <br />\n仲要請走個工人tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T18:49:31.000Z","msg":"我成日唔起屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccda4ce5f1a476ed518a237bf68570377933e749","tid":570570,"uid":97017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2537ec78bb454757c2ede7952136d6d3e6fffe9","tid":570